data.description: Welcome to your new home! Whether you're a buyer looking to move into a new home or an investor looking to invest in a property, this is right for you.  There is an enclosed front porch when you first enter the home. Next, you will enter a spacious living room that leads to the dining room and kitchen. The house also has a deck that needs some mending. Additionally, throughout the first floor, it has new hardwood. The house has quick access to SEPTA bus and subway services, is close to Central High School and LaSalle University, and is near Jefferson Einstein Hospital. Other local amenities include Explorers Den and Ron's Caribbean Cafe!
